{
  "stem": "6924.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And from there, we went to Wieliczka.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's in Wieliczka, they have a salt mine what's famous all over the world.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's on the ground with all different figures, and it was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So every year, we went someplace else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father-- it was quite expensive, but my father never said no to any excursion we had to make.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was always for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told me, any group-- you go with a group-- don't worry about it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll pay the bill.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] During this time, in the 1930s, Hitler came to power.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Did you hear about it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it's-- of course, I heard about Hitler, but I was young, and I really didn't realize what cloud came over Europe that would have started.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, as a boy in school, I didn't feel directly any-- any difference, you know, because in Poland, it started already-- the-- the government started to-- they used to say, economic we are-- we don't want to kill any Jews or any-- but-- but we want economic pressure is allowed, that's like-- I mean, against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it started to be felt.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But as a boy in school, I didn't feel it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Means-- it says in Polish, [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In other words, you can fight on the-- on the commerce, like against the Jews, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When it comes to do business, to discriminate against Jews, but not to deprive them of their life, you know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was following the German style when the Germans in the late '30s started to already to take away the businesses from Jews in Germany and expel them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It didn't affect my father, because my father was a small businessman, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
